sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant FE as Frontend (React)
  participant BE as Flask API
  participant CS as ChatService
  participant EC as EmotionClassifier
  participant KB as KnowledgeBaseRetriever
  participant DOCS as kb/docs/*.txt

  U->>FE: Type message
  FE->>BE: POST /chat {message}
  BE->>CS: generate_reply(message)

  opt Emotions enabled
    CS->>EC: predict_emotions(text, top_k=3)
    EC-->>CS: raw_emotions + labels
  end

  CS->>CS: detect_intent(text)
  CS->>CS: detect_topic(text)

  alt intent == info_question or symptom and KB enabled
    CS->>KB: search(text, top_k=2)
    KB->>DOCS: load/index if needed
    KB-->>CS: kb_hits + sources
  else no KB or not info/symptom
    CS-->>CS: skip KB
  end

  CS->>CS: compose reply + safety constraints
  CS-->>BE: ChatResult
  BE-->>FE: JSON {reply, emotions, raw_emotions, topic, intent, kb_sources}
  FE-->>U: Display reply
